This Video Showcase Final boss battle and all cutscenes  of Naruto vs Mecha Kyuubi Naruto Special in Naruto Shippuden: Ultimate Ninja Storm  Revolution.► from latest Manga. ナルト- 疾風伝ナルティメットストームレボリューションNaruto Hinata and Mecha Kurma Naruto  gameplay. This video storyline is based  on Naruto Shippuden Episodes 376/377 – Extra Edition: The Directive to Take the Nine Tails 

Mecha-Naruto changes its programmings and returns the Nine-Tails' chakra back to Naruto. As Mecha-Naruto bisects Mecha Kurma in half to protect Naruto, he activates a switch, causing Mecha-Kurama to appear and causes mayhem at Konohagakure. Mecha-Naruto encases itself onto Naruto and battle Mecha-Kurama but their attacks have no effect whatsoever. Mecha-Naruto ultimately sacrifices itself to destroy Mecha Nine-Tails.
